explanation: [0-0] A young woman dressed in a Santa Claus costume and wearing a Santa hat is sitting on a bed, looking down with a red Christmas stocking in her hands. The walls of the room are green and decorated with a world map, a robot poster and other decorations, and several plush toys are placed on the bed.

[0-10] The woman in the Santa costume pulls out a pink gift box from the Christmas stocking and holds it high with both hands. She opens her mouth wide, and the gift box in her hand falls because she didn't hold it steady. The woman puts her hands on her head, showing a helpless expression. Then the woman in the Santa costume takes the Christmas stocking with both hands, moves it upwards, and it also falls. The woman shows a helpless expression and lies back.
